{"tid":428881,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解有酒粒嘅人笑得咁甜","createTime":"2017-10-08T12:00:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T13:49:41.000Z","uid":46514,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"403c14367528fc8ae364e18e43a4cf3c67def2e5","tid":428881,"uid":46514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T12:00:12.000Z","msg":"中學嘅時候曾經暗戀一個男同學<br />\n佢笑起上嚟好陽光好燦爛<br />\n覺得佢對酒粒好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識啲有酒粒嘅女仔都係<br />\n普普通通咁微笑露出個酒粒<br />\n已經令人覺得佢笑得好燦爛好甜美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人都咁覺得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f94ba8c17a5fc3af25ef568cf07f967d5855ea61","tid":428881,"uid":46514,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T12:11:43.000Z","msg":"冇人鍾意有酒粒嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"f3e8ad2386e28e130679b05199a41a763e932472","tid":428881,"uid":89735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T12:29:01.000Z","msg":"唔關酒粒事架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8bb7d97bc019c2b3af9b7072e63d020c303a23e","tid":428881,"uid":46514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T12:41:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔關酒粒事架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但我覺得有酒粒/梨渦好加分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aaffb37a510ec263f997c2cda5de87f9c65d69c","tid":428881,"uid":127395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T12:42:27.000Z","msg":"肥仔有酒粒點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6718b6821984b89e8d29fd8ed74106ce0bd1f71","tid":428881,"uid":47168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T12:42:50.000Z","msg":"覺得係加分位<img src=\"/ass