=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前中學都有見過有個肥仔同學有梨渦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得幾可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可愛即係唔會鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇下咩肥仔啦，高大肥仔都有market嘅<br />\n我識個同學係矮肥仔細佬feel所以淨係覺得可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d0a442781ac32fb359447d56091d4e33fc2af4","tid":428881,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T12:52:08.000Z","msg":"靚仔靚女笑都甜架啦"},{"pid":"ab7d058e4334c350236ac5a54f045b64932af48f","tid":428881,"uid":127395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T12:52:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>肥仔有酒粒點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前中學都有見過有個肥仔同學有梨渦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得幾可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可愛即係唔會鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇下咩肥仔啦，高大肥仔都有market嘅<br />\n我識個同學係矮肥仔細佬feel所以淨係覺得可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢幾矮幾肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d19c67cf42fb906ab4afc74c3d853ce13979ba8b","tid":428881,"uid":46514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T12:57:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>靚仔靚女笑都甜架啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我暗戀嗰個男仔唔靚仔<br />\n但都覺得 好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過的確見嗰啲都樣唔差<br />\n但平時其他人笑我唔會聯想到「甜美」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afaa54a5e2fba4cad369279896a4d054d47dc805","tid":428881,"uid":46514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T12:59:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>肥仔有酒粒點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前中學都有見過有個肥仔同學有梨渦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得幾可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可愛即係唔會鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇下咩肥仔啦，高大肥仔都有market嘅<br />\n我識個同學係矮肥仔細佬feel所以淨係覺得可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢幾矮幾肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔太記得喇，同我差唔多或者矮過我，我諗都係米六左右。未去到痴肥嘅地步，但一定會話佢係肥，塊面都多肉，手指都肥嗰種。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過佢中學嗰陣已經有女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個女仔高佢成個頭，唔知後來散咗未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"213d01c08f89c14901245fb38c3a3e761ae75c8d","tid":428881,"uid":127395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T13:00:37.000Z","msg":"<blockq