,"uid":46514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T13:03:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>肥仔有酒粒點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前中學都有見過有個肥仔同學有梨渦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得幾可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可愛即係唔會鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇下咩肥仔啦，高大肥仔都有market嘅<br />\n我識個同學係矮肥仔細佬feel所以淨係覺得可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢幾矮幾肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔太記得喇，同我差唔多或者矮過我，我諗都係米六左右。未去到痴肥嘅地步，但一定會話佢係肥，塊面都多肉，手指都肥嗰種。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過佢中學嗰陣已經有女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個女仔高佢成個頭，唔知後來散咗未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能佢依家米八靚仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢中六嗰陣都唔高，難啲突然二次發育生到米八<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但可能瘦咗嘅，如果瘦返少返啲肉五官出返嚟又有個酒粒仔可能都吸引嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96b60fae15e621cce6e193070170be1f8fd769fa","tid":428881,"uid":46514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T13:06:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blo